948
00:39:24,740 --> 00:39:25,430
But they are as lethal...

949
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:26,030
Advance.

950
00:39:26,910 --> 00:39:27,350
They are like the real ones.

951
00:39:27,350 --> 00:39:27,580
Forward!

952
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:43,660
Leader.

953
00:39:43,910 --> 00:39:45,180
