980
00:41:34,030 --> 00:41:35,100
Please come with me.

981
00:41:36,580 --> 00:41:37,260
If that is the wish of the State Preceptor,

982
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:38,830
I shall comply.

983
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:40,100
Let's go.

984
00:41:55,620 --> 00:41:56,830
