♪To have a pristine soul in this polluted world♪

997
00:43:08,360 --> 00:43:10,020
♪Travel far♪

998
00:43:10,020 --> 00:43:12,540
♪And overcome challenges life throws at me♪

999
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:15,860
